    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>我们曾是敌人。我们曾摧毁整个世界。如今，我们是来创造的！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获取 Castle Crashers 画家魔王的天堂 DLC，让你的自定义角色鲜活起来！创造你的独特武士，在 Steam 创意工坊与大家分享，也可以化身全新官方角色：小小画家！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133920/extras/843aa491f869190e3156239195d66394.poster.avif?t=1754583799\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133920/extras/843aa491f869190e3156239195d66394.webm?t=1754583799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133920/extras/843aa491f869190e3156239195d66394.mp4?t=1754583799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DLC 特色内容：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 使用模板创建你的独特自定义角色，并与所有人分享！尽情创造吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 全新官方角色：化身小小画家，释放你的想象力，挥舞强大的艺术之笔，全面击溃敌人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 所有官方可玩角色和武器拥有全新艺术形象！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 主菜单视觉更新，共计 8 个场景绘就 Castle Crashers 的世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 全新地图美术，带你踏上绚烂的冒险之旅！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 丰富的武士选择：可以选择社区角色，也可以下载由我们的团队打造的官方角色！随心切换武士，尽情玩转角色！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也许你会怀念原版游戏的美术风格？别担心，前往主菜单可随时开启或关闭 DLC 特色功能，随时重温经典冒险！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133920/extras/810f78e29d29c680c43c0fe70601d3f9.avif?t=1754583799\" width=800 height=301 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以使用 DLC 模板设计自定义角色的头部、身体、武器、护盾、壮硕形态、外观以及“远离蛮族”相关部件！前往查阅 Steam 指南《如何使用画家魔王的天堂 DLC 模板创建自定义角色》，下载模板并开始创作吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133920/extras/d24a5b8990c791de956e08112c3d9a7f.poster.avif?t=1754583799\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133920/extras/d24a5b8990c791de956e08112c3d9a7f.webm?t=1754583799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133920/extras/d24a5b8990c791de956e08112c3d9a7f.mp4?t=1754583799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
